Day 50: Set Resource Limits in Kubernetes Pods

Date: October 16, 2025
Overview
Configured CPU and memory limits for pods.
Key Concepts Learned

Resource requests vs limits
Quality of Service (QoS) classes
Resource management
Node resource allocation

Commands Used
yamlresources:
  requests:
    memory: "64Mi"
    cpu: "250m"
  limits:
    memory: "128Mi"
    cpu: "500m"

Challenges Faced
Pods getting OOMKilled! Had to balance resource allocation carefully.
